a.title: Table outs.Affiliations Base table for affiliations/institutions (mag/Affiliations.txt)
Referred by Authors ( LastKnownAffiliationId -> AffiliationId ) Referred by PaperAuthorAffiliations ( AffiliationId )
Rank integer FROZEN; no new ranks are being added.
NormalizedName varchar UPDATED; slightly different normalization algorithm
GridId varchar FROZEN; ror_id is the new standard identifier for organizations
RorId varchar NEW; ROR for this organization, see https://ror.org, https://ror.org/:ror_id
PaperFamilyCount bigint FROZEN; same value as "paper_count.
Iso3166Code varchar Two-letter country codes, see https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_3166-2
UpdatedDate timestamp NEW; set values updated from new ror data
Table outs.AuthorExtendedAttributes Additional author name representations (mag/AuthorExtendedAttributes.txt)
AuthorId bigint FOREIGN KEY REFERENCES Authors.AuthorId
Table outs.Authors Base table for authors (mag/Authors.txt)
Referred by AuthorExtendedAttributes ( AuthorId ) Referred by PaperAuthorAffiliations ( AuthorId )
Rank integer FROZEN; no new ranks are being added
NormalizedName varchar UPDATED; slightly different normalization algorithm
Orcid varchar NEW; ORCID identifier for this author
PaperFamilyCount bigint FROZEN; same value as "paper_count
UpdatedDate timestamp NEW; set when changes are made going forward
Table outs.ConferenceInstances FROZEN; Base table for Conference Instances (mag/ConferenceInstances.txt)
NormalizedName varchar UPDATED; slightly different normalization algorithm
ConferenceSeriesId bigint FOREIGN KEY REFERENCES ConferenceSeries.ConferenceSeriesId
PaperFamilyCount bigint FROZEN; same value as "paper_count
Table outs.ConferenceSeries FROZEN; Base table for Conference Series (mag/ConferenceSeries.txt)
Referred by Papers ( ConferenceSeriesId ) Referred by ConferenceInstances ( ConferenceSeriesId )
Rank integer FROZEN; no new ranks are being added
NormalizedName varchar UPDATED; slightly different normalization algorithm
PaperFamilyCount bigint FROZEN; same value as "paper_count
Table outs.EntityRelatedEntities Relationship between papers, authors, fields of study. (advanced/EntityRelatedEntities.txt)
EntityType varchar Possible values: af (Affiliation), j (Journal), c (Conference)
RelatedEntityType varchar Possible values: af (Affiliation), j (Journal), c (Conference)
RelatedType integer Possible values: 0 (same paper), 1 (common coauthors), 2 (co-cited), 3 (common field of study), 4 (same venue), 5 (A cites B), 6 (B cites A)
Score real Confidence range between 0 and 1. Larger number representing higher confidence.
Table outs.FieldOfStudyChildren Relationship between Fields of Study (advanced/FieldOfStudyChildren.txt)
FieldOfStudyId bigint FOREIGN KEY REFERENCES FieldsOfStudy.FieldOfStudyId
ChildFieldOfStudyId bigint FOREIGN KEY REFERENCES FieldsOfStudy.FieldOfStudyId
Table outs.FieldOfStudyExtendedAttributes Other identifiers for Fields of Study (advanced/FieldOfStudyExtendedAttributes.txt)
FieldOfStudyId bigint FOREIGN KEY REFERENCES FieldsOfStudy.FieldOfStudyId

AttributeType bigint Possible values: 1 (AUI from UMLS https://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/licensedcontent/umlsarchives04.html#2018AA), 2 (source url), 3 (CUI from UMLS https://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/licensedcontent/umlsknowledgesources.html)
Table outs.FieldsOfStudy Base table for Fields of Study (advanced/FieldsOfStudy.txt)

Referred by FieldOfStudyChildren ( FieldOfStudyId ) Referred by FieldOfStudyChildren ( ChildFieldOfStudyId -> FieldOfStudyId ) Referred by RelatedFieldOfStudy ( FieldOfStudyId1 -> FieldOfStudyId ) Referred by RelatedFieldOfStudy ( FieldOfStudyId2 -> FieldOfStudyId ) Referred by FieldOfStudyExtendedAttributes ( FieldOfStudyId ) Referred by PaperFieldsOfStudy ( FieldOfStudyId )
Rank varchar FROZEN; no new ranks are being added.
NormalizedName varchar UPDATED; slightly different normalization algorithm
PaperFamilyCount bigint FROZEN; same value as "paper_count.
Table outs.Journals Base table for Journals (mag/Journals.txt)
Rank integer FROZEN; no new ranks are being added
NormalizedName varchar UPDATED; slightly different normalization algorithm
Issn varchar UPDATED; the ISSN-L for the journal (see https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International_Standard_Serial_Number#Linking_ISSN)
Issns varchar NEW; JSON list of all ISSNs for this journal (example: '["1469-5073","0016-6723"]' )
IsOa boolean NEW; TRUE when the journal is 100% OA
IsInDoaj boolean NEW; TRUE when the journal is in DOAJ (see https://doaj.org/)
PaperFamilyCount bigint FROZEN; same value as "paper_count
UpdatedDate timestamp NEW; set when changes are made going forward
PaperId bigint FOREIGN KEY REFERENCES papers.papers_id

Table outs.PaperAuthorAffiliations Links between papers, authors, and affiliations/institutions. NOTE: It is possible to have multiple rows with same (PaperId, AuthorId, AffiliationId) when an author is associated with multiple affiliations. (mag/PaperAuthorAffiliations.txt)
PaperId bigint FOREIGN KEY REFERENCES Papers.PaperId
AuthorId bigint FOREIGN KEY REFERENCES Authors.AuthorId
AffiliationId bigint FOREIGN KEY REFERENCES Affiliations.AffiliationId
AuthorSequenceNumber integer 1-based author sequence number. 1: the 1st author listed on paper, 2: the 2nd author listed on paper, etc.
PaperId bigint FOREIGN KEY REFERENCES papers.papers_id
PaperReferenceId bigint FOREIGN KEY REFERENCES papers.papers_id
PaperId bigint FOREIGN KEY REFERENCES Papers.PaperId
Table outs.PaperFieldsOfStudy Linking table from papers to fields, with score (advanced/PaperFieldsOfStudy.txt)
PaperId bigint FOREIGN KEY REFERENCES Papers.PaperId
FieldOfStudyId bigint FOREIGN KEY REFERENCES FieldsOfStudy.FieldOfStudyId
Score real Confidence range between 0 and 1. Bigger number representing higher confidence.
AlgorithmVersion integer NEW; version of algorithm to assign fields. Possible values: 1=old MAG (FROZEN), 2=OpenAlex
Table outs.PaperMeSH MeSH headings assigned to the paper by PubMed (advanced/PaperMeSH.txt)
PaperId bigint FOREIGN KEY REFERENCES Papers.PaperId
Table outs.PaperRecommendations Paper recommendations with score (advanced/PaperRecommendations.txt)
PaperId bigint FOREIGN KEY REFERENCES Papers.PaperId
RecommendedPaperId bigint FOREIGN KEY REFERENCES Papers.PaperId
Score real Confidence range between 0 and 1. Bigger number representing higher confidence.
Table outs.PaperReferences Paper references and, in reverse, citations (mag/PaperReferences.txt)
PaperId bigint FOREIGN KEY REFERENCES Papers.PaperId
PaperReferenceId bigint FOREIGN KEY REFERENCES Papers.PaperId
Table outs.PaperResources FROZEN; no longer updated. Data and code urls associated with papers (mag/PaperResources.txt)
PaperId bigint FOREIGN KEY REFERENCES papers.papers_id
SourceUrl varchar List of urls associated with the project, used to derive resource_url
Table outs.PaperUrls Urls for the paper (mag/PaperUrls.txt)
PaperId bigint FOREIGN KEY REFERENCES Papers.PaperId
UrlForLandingPage varchar NEW; URL for the landing page, when article is free to read
UrlForPdf varchar NEW; URL for the PDF, when article is free to read
HostType varchar NEW; host type of the free-to-read URL, Possible values: publisher, repository
Version varchar NEW; version of the free-to-read URL Possible values: submittedVersion, acceptedVersion, publishedVersion
License varchar NEW; license of the free-to-read URL (example: cc0, cc-by, publisher-specific)
RepositoryInstitution varchar NEW; name of repository host of URL
OaiPmhId varchar NEW; OAH-PMH id of the repository record
Table outs.Papers Main data for papers (mag/Papers.txt)

Referred by PaperUrls ( PaperId ) Referred by PaperResources ( PaperId ) Referred by PaperReferences ( PaperId ) Referred by PaperReferences ( PaperReferenceId -> PaperId ) Referred by PaperRecommendations ( PaperId ) Referred by PaperRecommendations ( RecommendedPaperId -> PaperId ) Referred by PaperMeSH ( PaperId ) Referred by PaperExtendedAttributes ( PaperId ) Referred by PaperCitationContexts ( PaperId ) Referred by PaperCitationContexts ( PaperReferenceId -> PaperId ) Referred by PaperAbstractsInvertedIndex ( PaperId ) Referred by PaperFieldsOfStudy ( PaperId ) Referred by PaperAuthorAffiliations ( PaperId )
Rank integer FROZEN; no new ranks are being added
Doi varchar Doi values are upper-cased per DOI standard at https://www.doi.org/doi_handbook/2_Numbering.html#2.4
DocType varchar Possible values: Book, BookChapter, Conference, Dataset, Journal, Patent, Repository, Thesis, NULL : unknown. Patent is FROZEN; no new Patents are being added.
Genre varchar NEW; Crossref ontology for work type such as "journal-article, posted-content, dataset, or book-chapter
IsParatext boolean NEW; indicates front-matter. See https://support.unpaywall.org/support/solutions/articles/44001894783
PaperTitle varchar UPDATED; slightly different normalization algorithm
JournalId bigint FOREIGN KEY references journals.journal_id
ConferenceSeriesId bigint FROZEN; no longer updated, no new Conference Series are being added. FOREIGN KEY references conference_series.conference_series_id.
ConferenceInstanceId bigint FROZEN; no longer updated, no new Conference Instances are being added. FOREIGN KEY references conference_instances.conference_instance_id.
FamilyId bigint FROZEN; no longer updated.
FamilyRank bigint FROZEN; no longer updated.
DocSubTypes varchar Possible values: Retracted Publication, Retraction Notice
OaStatus varchar NEW; Possible values: closed, green, gold, hybrid, bronze (see https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open_access#Colour_naming_system)
BestUrl varchar NEW; An url for the paper (see paper_urls table for more)
BestFreeUrl varchar NEW; Url of best legal free-to-read copy when it exists (see https://support.unpaywall.org/support/solutions/articles/44001943223)
BestFreeVersion varchar NEW; Possible values: submittedVersion, acceptedVersion, publishedVersion
DoiLower varchar NEW; lowercase doi for convenience linking to Unpaywall
UpdatedDate timestamp NEW; set when changes are made going forward
Table outs.RelatedFieldOfStudy Relationships between fields of study (advanced/RelatedFieldOfStudy.txt)
FieldOfStudyId1 bigint FOREIGN KEY REFERENCES FieldsOfStudy.FieldOfStudyId
Type1 varchar Possible values: general, disease, disease_cause, medical_treatment, symptom
FieldOfStudyId2 bigint FOREIGN KEY REFERENCES FieldsOfStudy.FieldOfStudyId
Type2 varchar Possible values: general, disease, disease_cause, medical_treatment, symptom
Rank real FROZEN; no new ranks are being added.
